=寒夜次潘岷源韻=

一片西風作楚聲
臥聞落葉打窗鳴
不知十月江寒重
陡覺三更布被輕

霜壓啼烏驚月上
夜驕饑鼠闞燈明
還家蒙繞江湖闊
薄醉醒來句忽成


A brise of western wind makes sounds from Chu,
lying i hear the falling leafs hitting the window.
I dont know that the october is so cold at the Jiang river,
suddenly i feel at the third double hour the [] quilt is thin.



